<body>
	<main>

		<div class="windowGroup">
		 {{#each window}}
		    <div id="window{{id}}" class="window">
		        <div class="purple">
		            <p class="windowTitle">{{Title}}</p>
		        </div>
		        <div class="mainWindow">
		            <div>
						<h3>{{Title}}</h3>
						<h4>{{Subtitle}}</h4>
						<p>{{disclaimer}}</p>
					</div>
					<div class="full_photo">
						<img src="./public/images/{{sectionSplashImg}}">
					</div>
					{{#each category}}
					<div>
						<h4>{{Title}}</h4>
						<div>
							<div>
								{{#each details}}
								<p>{{this}} </p>							
								{{/each}}
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					{{/each}}
		        </div>
		    </div>
		    {{/each}}
		</div>

			<div class="homeContent">
				<div class="intro">
							<h1>Karen Ma</h1>							
							<p>Senior Product Designer @ SingleStore — growth, security, developer experience.
							</p>
							<button><a href = "" target ="_blank"> Resume</a></button>
				</div>
				<div class= "proj">
					<h2>Selected Work</h2>
					{{#each project}}
					<div class="project">
						<div class= "projBlurbs">
						<button id="button{{id}}"><h3>{{Title}}</h3></button>
						<p>{{Subtitle}}</p>
						</div>	
					</div>
					{{/each}}
				</div>	
				<div class= "moreAbout">
					<h2>More</h2>
					<p>I started my career in product design because of my interest in Cognitive Science; I loved the interaction between the behavioral research and analytics and the technical applications of the field. Now, work keeps my engaged when I get to spend time discussing product strategy and product vision, writing new guidelines for design systems and growing design culture. Outside of work,I also mentor on <a href ="https://www.get-merit.com/p/karen-ma" target = "_blank">Merit </a>
					<p>In my spare time, I enjoy tinkering with all sorts of hands on crafts — currently lost wax casting. I'm currently thinking about <a href = "https://bookshop.org/p/books/the-poison-squad-one-chemist-s-single-minded-crusade-for-food-safety-at-the-turn-of-the-twentieth-century-deborah-blum/586737" target="_blank"> The Poison Squad</a>.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
	</main>
